      • string2URL

        static URL string2URL(String... strings)
        Converts a String into a URL without throwing a MalformedURLException. Instead such an exception will lead to an Logging.error(Throwable). So you should be very confident that your URL is well-formed when calling this method.
        Parameters:
        strings - the Strings describing the URL
        Returns:
        the URL that is constructed from the given string
